{"tid":1223945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近日網上轉載各懷疑冒警/冒記者事件整合","createTime":"2019-06-15T00:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T04:13:22.000Z","uid":24721,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b647ee3dcb2605c4c4f3a0c41fb55684eaa3eca0","tid":1223945,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:26:10.000Z","msg":"我太窮的後裔本身對於警方過份使用武力對待示威者都已經好不滿，但認為每個人做出左行為之後只要肯承擔個後果，都未算係最惡劣。<br />\n但係我宜家係見到一班身份未明既人濫用權力。使用各種佢地聲稱既身份既權利同權力達到目的，然後拍拍羅友，被害/被行使權力影響到既人無法追究，我就嬲到癲撚左。<br />\n<br />\n以下係客觀整合各事件:<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n來源: 譚文豪 Jeremy Tam<br />\n<br />\n片: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/858421787553638/posts/2328165767245892?s=100013531352677&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F858421787553638%2Fposts%2F2328165767245892%3Fs%3D100013531352677%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8NXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=af62cd38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/858421787553638/posts/2328165767245892?s=100013531352677&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n有巴打翻譯做英文，方便send比全世界:<br />\n#336神速失魂 &bull; 5h<br />\n英文字幕, 終於KO<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇中字sor<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/8ztesw8p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2F8ztesw8p&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8NXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=457c4cf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/8ztesw8p</a><br />\n<br />\n呢件事仲有巴打夢見當事人: <br />\nStandardWhey巴打:<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由於巴打原本係用加密方式post, 我都專重佢唔解密, 原post: <br />\n起埋呢條死黑警！警員證都唔敢show<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/OiLfxV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/OiLfxV</a><br />\n#15 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n巴打有安杏果都夢見另一個警員<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>蝗蟲樣黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Myqwxb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Myqwxb.png&h=4e5a42c0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>無認錯既話<br />\n呢隻黑警狗叫張建成<br />\n中同<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/974/sim/bottom.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F974%2Fsim%2Fbottom.htm&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8NXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=dbcd0886\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/974/sim/bottom.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n原post:<br />\n(突發) 問極班狗都攞唔出委任証<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/inqwzwX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/inqwzwX</a><br />\n#424 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n來源: Marcus Lau<br />\n片: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2413922815343553/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmlyc6%2Fvideos%2F2413922815343553%2F&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8NXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=36ebc73e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2413922815343553/</a><br />\n未有時間人物地點<br />\n<br />\n原post: <br />\n快backup 又一單冒警<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223521</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據網上多方分析表示警員不展示委任證而且其他警員亦縱容係有幾個原因<br />\n1. 警員不希望被投訴<br />\n2.根本就不持有有效警員委任證，懷疑冒警<br />\n<br />\n如為1. 則嚴重違紀。紀律部隊則毫無紀律可言，任何行為不受任何監管<br />\n留意番:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/822/chi/f01.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F822%2Fchi%2Ff01.htm&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8NXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=1a3eecec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/822/chi/f01.htm</a><br />\n（一）便衣人員與巿民接觸時，不論是否當值，在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。(PGO 20-16)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/13_faqs/faq_g.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F13_faqs%2Ffaq_g.html&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8NXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=1eebdea7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/13_faqs/faq_g.html</a><br />\n警察委任證特徵如下：<br />\n<br />\n正面印有(包括中英文) ：　　<br />\n香港警察、　　<br />\n彩色警徽、　　<br />\n警務人員姓名、職級、僱員號碼、　　<br />\n相片，另有香港警察及HONG KONG POLICE 字眼的鐳射標記。　<br />\n<br />\n背面印有以下聲明：「本證持有人是經正式委任的香港警察，其相片及資料載於背面。」<br />\n<br />\n(有關警察委任證之警訊片段&ndash; (冒警騙案))<br />\n<br />\n如2.屬實，巿民大眾的身家性命財產將受嚴重威脅！<br />\n更有分析指那些警員可能並非真正香港警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IKsSMog9hNE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIKsSMog9hNE&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8NXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=a838504d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IKsSMog9hNE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係同香港警察作對，<br />\n而係條例清清楚楚寫明規矩係點就要跟<br />\n唔係咩叫紀律部隊？<br />\n證都唔拎，話自己係警察就搜人身，行使警權，<br />\n憑既既唔係你既能力，唔係你既專業，<br />\n只係恃住你大聲，惡，人多，疊馬，<br />\n如果你真係警察，咁做只係自己侮辱緊警隊同自己，侮辱緊你所謂既紀律訓練。<br />\n放左工已經唔敢話自己做警察，做緊野都唔敢咁仲有咩意思？<br />\n希望作為警員既你地睇緊個post好好諗清楚自己做緊乜。"},{"pid":"59627aa190a34806d765c41acf68e9ae11d163ee","tid":1223945,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf30f65f3d64d77bd01182ddfbddbd0322f7678","tid":1223945,"uid":243834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:50:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d232518ca314363533a2fb0622f1fc2bd626910","tid":1223945,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:55:44.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n老臨食屎啦"},{"pid":"78e77276d21358a40d52df255e868c2cca5b9b8b","tid":1223945,"uid":38136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:27:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe4f03f8183577a0ca61fb987778791283bd8b9e","tid":1223945,"uid":201043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:28:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"669cb7f888912a245edaf99ba5e8cee0d30973be","tid":1223945,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\